OL,3,CPolice renew appeal five years after
OL,4,Cnewborn baby found dead in Walsall
OL,5,Ccanal
OL,7,FWest Midlands Police has renewed an
OL,8,Fappeal five years after the body of a
OL,9,Fnewborn baby boy was found in a canal
OL,10,Fin Walsall.
OL,12,FA passer-by spotted the baby in Rough
OL,13,FWood Country Park in Willenhall in May
OL,14,F2021.
OL,16,FWest Midlands Police said at the time
OL,17,Fits priority was to find the baby's
OL,18,Fmum, to make sure she's okay.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
