PN,37502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1779293476
OL,3,CPolice renew appeal five years after
OL,4,Cnewborn baby found dead in Walsall
OL,5,Ccanal
OL,7,FOn Wednesday 20 May 2026, the force
OL,8,Fsaid it's appealing to the local
OL,9,Fcommunity and the wider public to help
OL,10,Fthem get 'justice' for the baby boy.
OL,12,FHe was found in the Wryley and
OL,13,FEssington Canal at Rough Wood Country
OL,14,FPark near Willenhall on 20 May 2021.
OL,16,FOfficers say it is possible that the
OL,17,Fbaby may have been in the canal for a
OL,18,Ffew days.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
