CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1779293476
OL,3,CPolice renew appeal five years after
OL,4,Cnewborn baby found dead in Walsall
OL,5,Ccanal
OL,7,FMultiple appeals have been issued
OL,8,Fsince then, and the force says it's
OL,9,Facted on every bit of information it
OL,10,Fhas received.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Matt Marston, from
OL,13,FWest Midlands Police, said: "We
OL,14,Funderstand that it might be hard for
OL,15,Fsome people who have information to
OL,16,Fcontact us. We know this might be
OL,17,Fdifficult.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
